Information

Fake Britain: Series 7
Series which reveals the extent of fake goods in the UK, and investigates the conmen who are trying to get their hands on your money.


9)  Part 9 
This episode looks at the fake energy-saving schemes that are tricking customers, the fake concert tickets that ruined one couple's marriage plans, the huge business in fake TV remote controls and the fake children's illuminated balloons that prove to be dangerous.
